Bugs and feature requests please add to the issue tracker:
https://github.com/runlevel5/figpad/issues

figpad is based on l3afpad by Steven Honeyman,
https://github.com/stevenhoneyman/l3afpad

l3afpad is a GTK3 port of Leafpad by Tarot Osuji,
http://tarot.freeshell.org/leafpad/

leafpad authors:
  Tarot Osuji <tarot@sdf.lonestar.org>
  Wen-Yen Chuang (caleb) <caleb@calno.com>

l3afpad authors:
  Steven Honeyman <stevenhoneyman@gmail.com>
  Yoo, Taik-Yon <jaagar@gmail.com>

Artists:
  Lapo Calamandrei <calamandrei@gmail.com>
  Jack Gandy <scionicspectre@gmail.com>
